text:
Peddlers--Shoes: In a poor district of New York shoes are sold off the pushcarts and the sidewalk. View 1 is at 319 East 11th Street; view 2 at Park Avenue and East 11th Street.

P. L. Sperr

1934
views 1,2
title: Occupations - Peddlers - Shoes.
